    "In this experiment, only the data augmentation phase is removed from the proposed model, while the other phases are left.",
    "According to the findings in Table 1, the issue of overfitting in a CNN architecture can be successfully mitigated by applying a variety of data augmentation techniques, which enhances the overall model's performance.",
